{"tid":22423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡志偉：民主黨和梁振英誓不兩立","createTime":"2016-12-04T12:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T13:14:25.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de1e190389f1885a7b1580f4f9951c86af0c8320","tid":22423,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"胡志偉：民主黨和梁振英誓不兩立<br />\n2016-12-04 HKT 20:14<br />\n<br />\n民主黨舉行週年會員大會，改選新一屆領導層，包括正、副主席及中委會。胡志偉以282票當選民主黨主席，而副主席則由羅健熙和李永成擔任，他們分別得到222及209票。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉表示，首要工作是動員全黨上下及巿民向行政長官梁振英作全面還擊，他指，不能接受梁振英用公權介入立法會事務，民主黨和梁振英誓不兩立。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉又說，民主黨不會讓梁振英及建制派在議會予取予攜，將用一切方法阻止他連任。至於與中央溝通方面，胡志偉指民主黨不會抗拒就香港人的利益和事情與中央溝通，但中央要真正面對香港社會的問題，接受港人的看法。"},{"pid":"69253f0a334869488ad95897372c3b022ee9b0b7","tid":22423,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ee1c585da167e8ae935088c833445aba996ee85","tid":22423,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:20:54.000Z","msg":"淨係識反689同建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35ef4637fac79b6815900ba6e22fd36d5e6e54f","tid":22423,"uid":18313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21597e3303f2100ba1166cb2e8f64d2db84ef77","tid":22423,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"noted with thx"},{"pid":"f4db27a462d1f80c261a75b9650b4dfca670b157","tid":22423,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e61289d83eb81410cb4ff436137c17ecd2196e4","tid":22423,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"梁振英:好撚驚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7114bc95b311cf40034a892e141c28ff40fd017","tid":22423,"u